mary jane watson , often shortened to m.j. , is a fictional supporting character appearing originally in marvel comic books and later in multiple spin - offs and dramatizations of the spider - man titles as the best friend , love interest , and one - time wife ( as mary jane watson - parker ) of peter parker , the alter ego of spider - man , after the death of gwen stacy .

dinner & a movie : mary jane watson slings plates at the moondance diner in this 2002 superhero film

